{"tid":1999760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[韓戰]南韓稱有子彈射中非軍事區哨站　指北韓似乎非故意挑釁","createTime":"2020-05-03T11:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T13:25:01.000Z","uid":105567,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"84368977c95349bd4739533d14c16553c780af06","tid":1999760,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:31:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523989-20200503.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523989-20200503.htm&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgiaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=f27ba5d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523989-20200503.htm&h=97a291ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523989-20200503.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n南韓指出早上從北韓一方，有幾枚子彈射中非軍事區內南韓的監視哨站，南韓士兵開槍示警。<br />\n<br />\n南韓聯合參謀本部官員說，朝方似乎並非故意挑釁，又說事發時頗大霧，北韓軍人經常趁這個時候換班，目前未偵測到北韓軍方有任何異常舉動。南韓已透過軍事聯絡渠道要求北韓解釋，北韓暫時未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n事發在當地早上7時半後，南韓官員說接壤北韓邊境的鐵原郡，有駐守哨站的士兵聽到幾下槍聲，之後在哨站牆壁上見到4個彈孔。士兵按指引分兩次向北韓方向開了20槍示警，每次連續開10槍，再向北韓一方廣播；事件中南韓無人員傷亡，無設備受損，暫時未知北韓有無人死傷及設備受損。<br />\n<br />\n南韓軍方正詳細調查及蒐證，包括尋找子彈碎片，以及北韓方面開槍的動機。"},{"pid":"5b65bfd99fe5812d73d8184b4157f580f6b2649d","tid":1999760,"uid":87780,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:35:30.000Z","msg":"打到埋首爾都係友好行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"405056b01782ad5b3a5462a424971568affa5fda","tid":1999760,"uid":9193,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:38:45.000Z","msg":"非故意挑釁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1db5eb01c01b7c28c961d8538c01b72678a125f","tid":1999760,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike